commit_message: Merge branch 'PeerJ' of https://github.com/moss-lab/ScanFold into PeerJ
Merge branch 'PeerJ' of https://github.com/moss-lab/ScanFold into PeerJ
Update ScanFold.py and split functions out to separate script (ScanFoldFunctions.py)
removed "fold only" to to error (cause unknown)
Merge branch 'PeerJ' of https://github.com/moss-lab/ScanFold into PeerJ
Initial commit of "All in one" ScanFold script.

Merge pull request #8 from moss-lab/add-license-1

Create LICENSE
Removed Zika accesion number from write_bp
Added ability to consider hard constraints during scanning process (using "--constraints <.dbn constraint file>")
swiched bp track output for no competition
Changing script complete to different tab level
added function to write bp file for igv.js
removed pycurl and changed resuest url function
Adding requests function to set up call back to node
Trying to organize outfiles for argparse
Fixed shuffle, removed print to screen and write summary line
Fixed log file output to report competing base pair
Updated to allow negative or positive strand scans
Created optional quick method (dp file output instead of ct). Corrected ct file output for reverse strand genes from structurome
Allows ScanFold to parse negative strand gene csv files from structurome
Allowed RNAStructuromeDB csv downloads as input
Added extra ct2dot functions for additional ct outputs
Allowed CSV file type as input
Added function to convert CT files to DBN files (REQUIRES "import RNAStructure" on server)
Converted stdout log file to two written log files.
